title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 27 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 27 2022
description:
Matt Larkin, House candidate in Washington State's 8th district, joins Clay and Buck to discuss another winnable race for Republicans. C&B take a call from a ticked-off Ohio mom voting on a single issue: what covid restrictions did to her kids. Our favorite election nerd Ryan Girdusky, founder of the 1776 Project PAC, breaks down the key midterm races. Fetterman can't say "Statue of Liberty."

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
